---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Changelog - Marteso">
  <div class="page-header">
    <div class="section-label">Changelog</div>
    <h1>What's new in Marteso</h1>
    <p class="page-description">Every release, every improvement. We ship updates weekly — here's what we've built.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="subscribe-bar">
    <div class="subscribe-card">
      <p><strong>Stay in the loop.</strong> Get an email when we ship something new.</p>
      <div class="subscribe-form">
        <input type="email" class="subscribe-input" placeholder="you@example.com" />
        <a href="#" class="btn btn-secondary">Subscribe</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="changelog-section">

    <div class="changelog-entry">
      <div class="entry-meta">
        <div class="entry-date">Mar 2026</div>
        <div class="entry-version">v1.8.0</div>
      </div>
      <div class="entry-content">
        <div class="tags">
          <span class="tag tag-new">New</span>
          <span class="tag tag-improved">Improved</span>
        </div>
        <h2>Competitor Intelligence &amp; AI Review Summaries</h2>
        <p class="entry-summary">This release brings a completely rethought Competitor Intelligence module, plus AI-generated weekly summaries for your review inbox — so you can understand user sentiment at a glance without reading hundreds of reviews.</p>
        <ul class="change-list">
          <li><div class="change-dot new"></div>New Competitor Intelligence dashboard: metadata change history, keyword movement, and review trends for any tracked app</li>
          <li><div class="change-dot new"></div>AI review summaries — weekly digest of your top themes, complaints, and feature requests generated by Claude</li>
          <li><div class="change-dot new"></div>Keyword gap report: automatically highlights keywords your competitors rank for that you don't</li>
          <li><div class="change-dot improved"></div>Rank tracking page redesign — faster to navigate, cleaner sparklines, sortable by movement</li>
          <li><div class="change-dot improved"></div>Metadata editor now shows keyword density alongside character counts</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="changelog-entry">
      <div class="entry-meta">
        <div class="entry-date">Feb 2026</div>
        <div class="entry-version">v1.7.0</div>
      </div>
      <div class="entry-content">
        <div class="tags">
          <span class="tag tag-new">New</span>
          <span class="tag tag-fixed">Fixed</span>
        </div>
        <h2>Autonomous Mode &amp; Dark Theme</h2>
        <p class="entry-summary">Autonomous Mode lets Marteso take proactive actions on your behalf — flagging keyword opportunities, suggesting metadata edits, and drafting review responses — all surfaced in a single action queue you approve with one click.</p>
        <ul class="change-list">
          <li><div class="change-dot new"></div>Autonomous Mode: AI-powered action queue for proactive ASO recommendations</li>
          <li><div class="change-dot new"></div>Dark theme is now the default across all pages and emails</li>
          <li><div class="change-dot new"></div>Slack integration for rank alerts and autonomous action notifications</li>
          <li><div class="change-dot improved"></div>Weekly report emails redesigned — mobile-optimized, cleaner layout</li>
          <li><div class="change-dot fixed"></div>Fixed an issue where Google Play keyword ranks were delayed by up to 36 hours</li>
          <li><div class="change-dot fixed"></div>Fixed: adding an app via its Play Store URL now correctly identifies the package name</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="changelog-entry">
      <div class="entry-meta">
        <div class="entry-date">Jan 2026</div>
        <div class="entry-version">v1.6.0</div>
      </div>
      <div class="entry-content">
        <div class="tags">
          <span class="tag tag-new">New</span>
          <span class="tag tag-improved">Improved</span>
        </div>
        <h2>A/B Testing &amp; Landing Page Redesign</h2>
        <p class="entry-summary">A/B testing is now available to all Pro users. Run experiments on icons, screenshots, and descriptions with automatic statistical significance detection. We also shipped a major landing page redesign.</p>
        <ul class="change-list">
          <li><div class="change-dot new"></div>A/B testing module for store listing experiments with significance reporting</li>
          <li><div class="change-dot new"></div>Real screenshot integration in the hero — shows your actual app dashboard</li>
          <li><div class="change-dot new"></div>Country selector on keyword search — now defaults to your app's primary market</li>
          <li><div class="change-dot improved"></div>Onboarding flow reduced from 6 steps to 3</li>
          <li><div class="change-dot improved"></div>Keyword difficulty scores recalibrated — now more accurate for niche categories</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="changelog-entry">
      <div class="entry-meta">
        <div class="entry-date">Dec 2025</div>
        <div class="entry-version">v1.5.0</div>
      </div>
      <div class="entry-content">
        <div class="tags">
          <span class="tag tag-new">New</span>
          <span class="tag tag-improved">Improved</span>
          <span class="tag tag-fixed">Fixed</span>
        </div>
        <h2>Multi-App Dashboard &amp; Bulk Keyword Import</h2>
        <p class="entry-summary">Managing multiple apps is now much faster. The new multi-app overview shows all your apps and their KPIs at a glance, and bulk keyword import via CSV cuts setup time for new apps from hours to minutes.</p>
        <ul class="change-list">
          <li><div class="change-dot new"></div>Multi-app overview dashboard with consolidated KPIs</li>
          <li><div class="change-dot new"></div>Bulk keyword import via CSV — up to 500 keywords at once</li>
          <li><div class="change-dot new"></div>Review response templates — save and reuse common responses</li>
          <li><div class="change-dot improved"></div>App selector in the nav bar replaces the previous app switcher modal</li>
          <li><div class="change-dot improved"></div>API response times improved by 40% across all ranking endpoints</li>
          <li><div class="change-dot fixed"></div>Fixed sentiment analysis misclassifying some emoji-heavy reviews as negative</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="changelog-entry">
      <div class="entry-meta">
        <div class="entry-date">Nov 2025</div>
        <div class="entry-version">v1.4.0</div>
      </div>
      <div class="entry-content">
        <div class="tags">
          <span class="tag tag-new">New</span>
        </div>
        <h2>Review Management &amp; Sentiment Analysis</h2>
        <p class="entry-summary">The review inbox launched in this release, bringing all App Store and Google Play reviews into a single place with AI-powered sentiment categorization and topic clustering.</p>
        <ul class="change-list">
          <li><div class="change-dot new"></div>Unified review inbox for App Store and Google Play</li>
          <li><div class="change-dot new"></div>AI sentiment analysis: positive / neutral / negative with confidence scores</li>
          <li><div class="change-dot new"></div>Topic clustering — automatically groups reviews by theme (onboarding, crashes, UX, etc.)</li>
          <li><div class="change-dot new"></div>Rating history charts per app version</li>
          <li><div class="change-dot improved"></div>Keyword research results now include trend direction over 30 / 90 days</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="changelog-entry">
      <div class="entry-meta">
        <div class="entry-date">Sep 2025</div>
        <div class="entry-version">v1.0.0</div>
      </div>
      <div class="entry-content">
        <div class="tags">
          <span class="tag tag-new">Launch</span>
        </div>
        <h2>Marteso is live</h2>
        <p class="entry-summary">Marteso launched publicly with keyword research, rank tracking, metadata editing, and competitor monitoring. Free Starter plan available from day one.</p>
        <ul class="change-list">
          <li><div class="change-dot new"></div>Keyword research with volume &amp; difficulty scores for 180+ countries</li>
          <li><div class="change-dot new"></div>Daily rank tracking for App Store and Google Play</li>
          <li><div class="change-dot new"></div>Metadata editor with character counters and keyword density</li>
          <li><div class="change-dot new"></div>Competitor tracking — monitor any app's rankings and ratings</li>
          <li><div class="change-dot new"></div>App Store Connect &amp; Google Play Console OAuth integration</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  .subscribe-bar {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto 64px;
    padding: 0 32px;
  }

  .subscribe-card {
    background: var(--bg-secondary);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 20px 24px;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 32px;
  }

  .subscribe-card p { font-size: 14px; color: var(--text-secondary); }
  .subscribe-card strong { color: var(--text-primary); }

  .subscribe-form { display: flex; gap: 10px; flex-shrink: 0; }

  .subscribe-input {
    background: var(--bg-primary);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 6px;
    padding: 8px 14px;
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    width: 200px;
    outline: none;
  }

  .subscribe-input::placeholder { color: var(--text-tertiary); }

  .changelog-section {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto 120px;
    padding: 0 32px;
  }

  .changelog-entry {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 120px 1fr;
    gap: 48px;
    padding: 48px 0;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .changelog-entry:first-child { border-top: none; }

  .entry-meta { padding-top: 4px; }

  .entry-date {
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--text-tertiary);
    font-family: 'SF Mono', monospace;
    margin-bottom: 6px;
  }

  .entry-version {
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--accent);
    font-family: 'SF Mono', monospace;
  }

  .tags { display: flex; gap: 6px; margin-bottom: 16px; }

  .tag {
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 600;
    padding: 2px 8px;
    border-radius: 4px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }

  .tag-new { background: var(--accent-dim); color: var(--accent); }
  .tag-improved { background: var(--accent-blue-dim); color: var(--accent-blue); }
  .tag-fixed { background: rgba(74,222,128,0.12); color: #4ade80; }

  .entry-content h2 {
    font-size: 22px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  .entry-summary {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .change-list {
    list-style: none;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 10px;
  }

  .change-list li {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 10px;
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .change-dot {
    width: 8px;
    height: 8px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    margin-top: 5px;
  }

  .change-dot.new { background: var(--accent); }
  .change-dot.improved { background: var(--accent-blue); }
  .change-dot.fixed { background: #4ade80; }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .changelog-entry { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 16px; }
    .subscribe-card { flex-direction: column; align-items: flex-start; }
    .subscribe-form { width: 100%; }
    .subscribe-input { flex: 1; }
  }
</style>
